title.narrative: Strengthening Malaria Monitoring and Evaluation Systems (SMMES)

description.narrative: (Ethiopia): The Strengthening Malaria Monitoring and Evaluation Systems activity provides the National Malaria Control Program with key technical assistance, operational research, monitoring and evaluation support and data management capacity building. The purpose is to strengthen malaria programming and facilitate implementation of the National Strategic Plan for malaria. Major activities include: .Monitoring and evaluation in the implementation of the national plan.Expanding malaria epidemic surveillance activities.Conducting and coordinating operational research, formative evaluations, and special studies including the malaria indicator survey.Providing carefully-selected technical assistance at national and regional levels in the areas of proposal development, strategic document preparation, and program management
